name: Kasa Central
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: $KASA is a full-stack toolbox & multi-function marketplace, Connecting Investors to Projects, We are currently developing various infrastructures for ICO, IGO, NFT, GameFi, Metaverse, Lottery, High stake Earnings, Cross-chain Bridge Aggregator, less fee transaction exchange and more. Our mission is to become the full-stack toolbox to help developers and users enclasp the crypto economy.
